-- KfW Agrees to Help Finance Yemeni Water Investments, Saba Says
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2012-12-13T17:18:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-13/kfw-agrees-to-help-finance-yemeni-water-investments-saba-says.html
KfW, the state-owned German
development bank, granted Yemen 12 million euros ($16 million)
to help finance water and sanitation projects in Abyan province,
Yemen’s state-run Saba news agency said, citing a ministerial
agreement signed with the bank in Sana’a.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in London at 
